# SmartCV Backend API Endpoints

Here is the list of available API endpoints for testing with Postman.

## Authentication & User Management
**Base URL**: `/users`

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Payload (Body) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/users/register` | Register a new user | `UserCreateRequest` (JSON) |
| `POST` | `/users/login` | Login | `AuthenticationRequest` (JSON) |
| `POST` | `/users/refresh` | Refresh JWT Token | `RefreshRequest` (JSON) |
| `POST` | `/users/logout` | Logout | `LogoutRequest` (JSON) |
| `POST` | `/users/Change-password` | Change Password | `ChangePasswordRequest` (JSON) |
| `GET` | `/users/list` | Get list of users | - |
| `GET` | `/users/{id}` | Get user by ID | - |
| `POST` | `/users/UpdateUser/{id}` | Update user details | `UserUpdateRequest` (FormData) |
| `DELETE` | `/users/{id}` | Delete user | - |

